Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.39,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are {\i1}always{\i0\fscx30} {\r} in a rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.94,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you locked up, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.69,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.02,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be set free soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.98,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go through the formalities later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.44,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.91,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after these blockheads for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.62,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Don't trust Kimblee too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.04,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why? He's a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.76,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rockbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:43.55,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents were the doctors who lost their lives at Ishbal, were they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.01,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.02,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:52.40,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It was my unit who recovered their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:57.78,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,We were a second too late.\NWhen we arrived at the scene, they were already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.78,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:06.29,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,They obeyed the ethics of medicine and\Nstuck to their convictions until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.20,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I admire them from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.67,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have met them while they were still with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:21.80,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,They kept a picture that was taken with an adorable little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.68,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence must have been what drove them onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.15,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance, Miss Winry Rockbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you know what he did at Ishbal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:49.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've only heard the true stories about Ishbal from the Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,From the Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:57.63,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with Winry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Just think about something else, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hydrogen, helium, lithium, beryllium...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...carbon, nitrogen, oxygen, sulfur...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.82,Default-alt,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,E-Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}...aluminum, silicon, phosphorus, chromium, manganese, iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...cobalt, nickel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.32,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I fall for a weirdo like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.95,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:37.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you, I told you to let me know before you join the nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever. Now for your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't its durability suffer if you make it so light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:56.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at the big picture, it's less durable than it used to be, but the key points have been reinforced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.44,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you out of your cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can think of it as\Nmy capability as a State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.54,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,You finally switched to a northern type?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got some changes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.87,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,This suits me the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:23.84,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Light-weight combat automail, M-1910!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.18,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The tip of your nails are reinforced!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.39,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's made out of diamond?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:35.18,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's a Neo M-1910, Mad Bear G!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.40,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Want me to equip you with something like this, Ed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.94,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,So who is this pretty gal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She's my mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.33,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What an ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.76,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've actually seen a northern automail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.51,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.34,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.68,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you want to look around my workplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.35,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes, I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.51,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too carried away and walk around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of dangerous around here. In a lot of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.73,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. I won't. Thanks for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.36,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for allowing me to look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.86,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,This one right here is pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:34.08,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is amazing! Isn't this a Crocodile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.58,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.24,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx93}She's so spirited about her work, just like how her parents were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.91,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,The thing really setting this apart from others is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.17,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx97}...it was designed with the material's expansion rate in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:44.63,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since your limbs are good to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.88,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...let's get down to business...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.88,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...Mr. Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...why can't {\i1}I{\i0\fscx30} {\r} be let out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.14,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kimblee's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:04.36,Default,Jel,0000,0000,0000,,We've been told to only release the Fullmetal Alchemist for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee's men...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:11.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They thought this through, not letting us work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:17.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They've also taken the effort to bring Winry here to show us that she's in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that shows how cautious they are about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't rush this. I have to wait for the right chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.38,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,The advance unit only brought enough food for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.09,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a week since they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.26,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,They could be on the verge of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.39,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried about their sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.02,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Being in complete darkness for an entire week is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.89,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Let us put our trust in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:48.40,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,General, there's no knowing what could happen down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.53,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't return in twenty-four hours, please seal this entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.53,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.13,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're all here, I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.80,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The murder of Lieutenant General Raven was my decision and act, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:13.30,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You all didn't see or hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:18.05,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If word gets out, blame everything on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.31,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:36.91,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.42,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Looks like things are starting to get hectic up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.17,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're going to have to start taking the initiative from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.68,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Briggs is staffed with men well-versed in defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:09:00.43,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Only one who excels in both offense and defense can snatch a victory by making the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:06.98,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx92}Which is why Madam Olivier believes that working with the\NEastern Army, well-versed in offensive tactics, is the best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:11.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to be selected as a partner for her tag team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.19,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:18.66,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,She said she just wants the power of the Eastern Army, and she'd rather you take a hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:28.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you this, though. What if I sold this information to the Führer President for my own gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.96,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,"Impossible. Mustang wouldn't do that," so she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.72,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 35,000 cenz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.18,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, who are you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:49.48,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Just a florist who's worked with the Armstrongs for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:10:05.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes, it seems the people who truly understand and support you are the ones who fought beside you in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What to do with these flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.62,Default-alt,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.67,Default-alt,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.13,Default-alt,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, god! He's looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.55,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as Smith's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.01,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Even metal has been cut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.60,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Stay on your toes. The enemy may still be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.61,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.16,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.58,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lieutenant Henshel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.17,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.46,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.17,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone else is in... p-pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We... We have to get out of here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That thing will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.26,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,"That thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow... The shadow will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:07.89,Default-alt,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.52,Default-alt,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.06,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.11,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:21.78,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.07,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Carry as many men as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.83,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for visiting so late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.33,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to deliver an urgent document to the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.46,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.51,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,He's not at home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.80,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like him to look through these by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.68,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,By tomorrow, right? I'll let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.35,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very mu-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.14,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You were still awake, Selim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:56.77,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard the door open,\Nso I thought Father might have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.65,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,This is Lieutenant Hawkeye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.24,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Miss Hawkeye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.78,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.20,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always work such late hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:09.24,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I've come to deliver a document to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:13.12,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for waking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:19.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Selim. You must sleep now, or you'll have a difficult time waking up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.55,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.09,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a bright boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.85,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're very proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:35.56,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You could call me an indulgent mother if he were my real child, but since he's an orphan, I can boast all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:42.28,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's distantly related to my husband, so it could be his blood that made him so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.41,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,He's not related to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.32,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:13:00.80,Default,Haw,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Colonel, King Bradley was raised as a test subject since he was an infant and has no blood relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.26,Default,Haw,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have any distant relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.18,Default,Haw,0000,0000,0000,,And that feeling I sensed earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:07.55,Default,Haw,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.30,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.64,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that mother of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.19,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,She just loves to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.61,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed a hint of bloodlust earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.69,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt the same sensation before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.70,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,And I just remembered where it was from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:30.20,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same sensation I felt when a Homunculus by the name of Gluttony snuck up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.20,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Selim Bradley...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:42.59,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite the nerve to ask me that in this situation, Lieutenant Hawkeye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.51,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,It's also smart of you not to pull out your gun, which you're so skilled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.39,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,You can't defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.31,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also a Homunculus, like Gluttony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.65,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,No, I sense a power that can hardly be compared to that of Gluttony's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.61,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be offended if you put me on the same level as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:11.70,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Pride. The First Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.09,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The First Homunculus, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.21,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.67,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly as the words mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:32.64,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,So you're planning on gathering as much information as you can, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.72,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a brave one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:38.35,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:39.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.90,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You just want another pawn, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.69,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:45.90,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.33,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cut the empty threats already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.75,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,There's no benefit in killing a hostage, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.83,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you saw through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.34,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,However, Lieutenant Hawkeye...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:11.43,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching you from your shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.61,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as a State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.53,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You have three tasks from the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:37.04,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Your first task is to search for Scar. All you have to do is find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.33,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of him after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:45.38,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Your second task is to look for Doctor Marcoh, who is presumed to be escaping alongside Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Marcoh is with Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.42,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Just like with your previous task,\Nafter you find him, I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:55.05,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Then, your third task is to carve a bloody crest into Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Carve a bloody crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.89,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.77,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Slaughtering humans and carving a symbol of hatred and sorrow into the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.99,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You became a dog of the military without the resolve to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,With the resolve {\i1}not{\i0\fscx30} {\r} to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.62,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,With a resolve not to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.34,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That can also be true, if you stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:33.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lending them a hand,\Nknowing what those guys are up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.34,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see how the world will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Resolve pitted against resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.10,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Will clashing against will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.43,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Life against life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,And humans against the Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:47.48,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Who will win? Which will the world choose as the victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:55.57,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,If humans are defeated by Homunculi, those who claim to be an evolved form of them, it's truly a historical moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.70,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to live to see that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you, a human, working with the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:07.50,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Because they'll let me use my alchemy as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.55,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:18.89,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,But if someone like me survives this,\Nthen it means the world's selected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.30,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle for existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.27,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,How worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.94,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:39.57,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought all alchemists were selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:45.16,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try appealing to your selfish side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.88,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Here's something you want more than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.88,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,If you accept the job, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk it over with Al and Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.69,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,With Miss Winry, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told her anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:15.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever job I may have to do,\NI don't want to lie to her and betray her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.03,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.91,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be monitoring you, so you don't tell her anything she doesn't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're currently being kept as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.05,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.68,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:46.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've been instructed by the higher-ups to do my duty as a human weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So I may have to be party to mass murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.69,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.86,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But can't you just refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.78,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:05.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm being a burden to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.79,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.54,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.54,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just mad at myself for being so happy-go-lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.59,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You two just want to get your bodies back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They'll give us a philosopher's stone if I help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What? A stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.68,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but those stones are made of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to take the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me look for Scar first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.71,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Scar killed Winry's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I want to avenge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.10,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be taking Al with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's in that state, Scar can't use his destruction techniques on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.23,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.98,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay, Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:26.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone is made by sacrificing the lives of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother isn't planning to use it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:42.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're thinking that there may be a way to get\Nour bodies back by using Eastern Alchemy from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:47.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And a little girl who can use\NEastern Alchemy is supposedly with Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.97,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,So he's making it look like he's going after Scar, but his plan is to get in touch with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's my guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.06,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.53,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd better think up a good reason, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.88,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to head to the location Scar was last sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.38,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, scoot in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.84,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Al, scoot over some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:36.89,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Winry, please wait at the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.69,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.06,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.53,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But I just fixed up his automail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.86,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if it stopped working all of a sudden, so I should go along in case maintenance is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.87,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to happen, it would hurt the proud name of the Rockbells!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're really into your work, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You workaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.21,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.63,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx93}We've been in business since my great-grandfather's generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:05.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're from a family of machine freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.63,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:04.71,Default-alt,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:06.72,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you call me a machine freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's no knowing what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:20.48,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:25.53,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sick of sitting and waiting for something to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:05.17,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,An all-out war between chimeras and humans takes place in a mining town where the piercing wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:08.80,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let down your guard. Give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:13.22,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,What is the strange aftermath brought forth by the fierce battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:18.31,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:22.31,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 38, Conflict at Baschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:26.19,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Humans let down their guard in their moments of victory.
